data.description: This home is in a great neighborhood, The Meadows across the street from Windstone Golf Course Community and less than a mile from 2 grocery stores Food City and Publix.  This wonderful home has a great floor plan with 3 Bedrooms on the main living area and a Bonus room that could be a 4th bedroom.  The bedrooms are split and the primary bedroom is by the kitchen so you don't have to walk very far to get your first cup of coffee.  The dining room is separate and is a good size with hardwood flooring.  The great room is wonderful  for entertaining along with a gas log fireplace and hardwood flooring.  Enjoy your days and evenings on your good size screened in porch looking out to your fenced in backyard.  Take a walk around the property virtually to see the complete lay out of the home.  Seller replaced the HVACs 1st floor in 2020 and 2nd floor in 2021.
